datasets.title: Population by country 2023
datasets.description: The dataset contains the population of all countries in the world for the year 2023. The dataset contains the population, ranking , land area and population density of all countries in the world. With the help of this dataset, we can find the population of any country in the world. The dataset is in JSON format.
